1
00:00:01,060 --> 00:00:02,460
Previously:
前情提要：

2
00:00:02,730 --> 00:00:06,330
There's this woman that I like a lot.
我很喜欢一个女人

3
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,760
But it's complicated.
事情很复杂

4
00:00:08,940 --> 00:00:12,340
She was with this other guy for a long time.
她跟另一个男人 交往了很久

5
00:00:12,570 --> 00:00:15,910
I could never do that to the guy. We're friends.
我没办法那样对他 我们是好朋友

6
00:00:16,110 --> 00:00:20,280
So this guy she used to go out with, is he a good guy?
以前跟她交往过的那个男人 他是好人吗？

7
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:23,140
The best.
他是最棒的

8
00:00:23,350 --> 00:00:25,910
-Then talk to him. -I don't know.
-跟他谈一谈 -我不知道

9
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:29,450
It's worth finding out, if you like her.
如果你喜欢她 这值得试一试

10
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:31,320
I do, so much.
我真的非常喜欢她

11
00:00:31,590 --> 00:00:34,320
I can't stop thinking about her. I can't sleep..
我没办法不想到她 我睡不着…

12
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:38,000
You know what? You have to go for it.
你知道吗？ 你得尽力去争取

13
00:00:38,230 --> 00:00:43,030
How often does this happen to you? You owe it to yourself.
你常遇到这种事吗？ 你应该为自己这么做的

14
00:00:44,270 --> 00:00:46,170
It's Rachel.
是瑞秋

15
00:00:55,620 --> 00:00:59,250
I'm sorry, did you just say it's Rachel?
对不起 你刚刚说是瑞秋吗？

16
00:01:00,690 --> 00:01:02,350
Yes.
对

17
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:07,190
You like Rachel?
你喜欢瑞秋？

18
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:12,360
Yes. I like Rachel.
对，我喜欢瑞秋

19
00:01:19,510 --> 00:01:21,070
Rachel?!
瑞秋

20
00:01:21,580 --> 00:01:24,640
Yeah. Okay, but look, you know..
对，听着，你知道的…

21
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:27,210
You know who else I like? You.
你知道我还喜欢谁吗？你

22
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:31,210
And it doesn't get said enough. I like you, Ross.
光说还是不够的 我喜欢你，罗斯

23
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:35,920
-"Rachel" Rachel? -It's not a big deal.
-那个“瑞秋”？ -没什么大不了的

24
00:01:36,090 --> 00:01:39,580
It's not a big deal? I'm sorry, I just..
没什么大不了的？ 抱歉，我只是…

25
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:43,060
What about the stuff you said?
你刚刚说的那些话呢？

26
00:01:43,330 --> 00:01:48,000
How you can't stop thinking about her? How you can't sleep?
你说你无法不去想她 你说你睡不着

27
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,030
I'm an actor, you know?
我是个演员，你知道吗？

28
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:54,170
As a group, we tend to be overdramatic.
演员习惯了夸张

29
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:57,610
Rachel-who's-carrying-my-baby Rachel?
怀着我孩子的瑞秋？

30
00:01:57,850 --> 00:02:01,210
I know it's bad. And I know it's wrong, okay?
我知道那很糟糕 我知道那是不对的，好吗？

31
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:04,540
It's not like anything's ever gonna happen.
那是不可能会发生的事

32
00:02:04,820 --> 00:02:07,750
These are just feelings. They'll go away.
那只是我的感觉 它们会消失的

33
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,520
You know, I gotta go.
我得走了

34
00:02:10,760 --> 00:02:12,060
Hey, Ross..
罗斯

35
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:16,220
You know, I just have one-- Rachel?!
我只是有个… 瑞秋？

36
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,540
Rachel?!
瑞秋？

37
00:02:31,618 --> 00:02:33,813
The One Where Joey Tells Rachel
本集播出：乔依告诉瑞秋

00:02:34,618 --> 00:02:35,813
rainystar压制iPod-MP4

38
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:11,050
Okay, she's kicking.
她在踢我

39
00:03:11,950 --> 00:03:14,480
She's growing inside you.
她在你的体内成长

40
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:20,520
-That was a big one. -That's the youngest girl to reject me.
-这一下踢得好用力 -她是拒绝我的最年轻的女孩

41
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,950
-You guys! -Hey there.
-大家好 -嗨

42
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:26,460
Let me ask you. Do you believe in soul mates?
我要问你们 你们相信有心灵伴侣吗？

43
00:03:26,730 --> 00:03:27,960
Oh, yes, I do.
我相信

44
00:03:28,170 --> 00:03:30,970
There's one person out there for everyone.
每个人都有失落的另一半

45
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:34,170
You know how you find him? Stop looking.
你知道你该怎么找到他吗？ 停止再找了

46
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:37,430
I've stopped looking for Russell Crowe.
我已经停止寻找罗素克洛

47
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,480
He'll find me.
他会找到我的

48
00:03:39,650 --> 00:03:40,880
And you?
你呢？

49
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:46,280
No. I believe that certain people are more suited for each other, but..
不，我相信有些人 非常适合彼此，但是…

51
00:03:46,490 --> 00:03:49,120
-Soul mates? I don't think they exist. -Good.
-心灵伴侣？我想他们并不存在 -很好

52
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:52,120
-Why? -Well, last night, I met Monica's.
-为什么？ -昨晚我遇到了摩妮卡的心灵伴侣

53
00:03:56,970 --> 00:03:58,190
What?
什么？

54
00:03:58,470 --> 00:04:02,330
I had a date with this guy. I swear he's her other half.
我跟这个男的约会 我发誓他是她的另一半

55
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:07,700
You don't think there's somebody better suited for Monica than me?
你不觉得会有人 比我更适合摩妮卡吧？

56
00:04:10,850 --> 00:04:12,870
Well, what's he like?
他长什么样子？

57
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:16,510
-He's tall. He has brown hair. -Of course.
-他很高，是棕发 -当然

58
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:21,180
A tall guy with hair similar to mine? Oh, unknowable universe!
一个发色跟我一样的高大男人？ 宇宙真的是太大了

59
00:04:21,860 --> 00:04:24,420
-He works with food. -Oh, sure. Older?
-他从事跟食物相关的行业 -当然，他比较老吗？

60
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:28,190
-Obviously. And he's British. -I was just gonna ask!
-没错，他是英国人 -我正打算要问你

61
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:32,860
And he's so centered, and mature and confident.
他非常聪明 成熟有自信

62
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:35,540
It's so sad they never met.
真可惜他们不认识彼此

63
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:40,300
Luckily, the guy she settled for can't hear you.
还好她老公没听到你那么说

64
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:43,340
Oh, I'm so sorry. Maybe I'm wrong.
抱歉 或许我错了

65
00:04:43,580 --> 00:04:46,510
We're going out again. I'll find out more.
我们会再约会 我会把他调查得更仔细

66
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:49,680
He's meant for her, and you're gonna date him?
他跟别人是天生一对 你还要跟他约会？

67
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:53,120
He may not be my soul mate, but a girl's gotta eat.
或许他不是我的心灵伴侣 但我总得吃饭吧

68
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,350
Rachel?!
瑞秋

69
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,290
I didn't know Joey was on JAG.
我不知道乔伊演过《执法悍将》

70
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,740
-Hey. -Hey.
-嘿 -嘿

71
00:05:18,010 --> 00:05:21,240
I talked to Joey. I wanted to see you.
我刚跟乔伊谈过 我想知道你好不好

72
00:05:21,450 --> 00:05:25,550
I still can't believe it. Joey and Rachel?
我还是不敢相信 乔伊跟瑞秋？

73
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:28,880
It's like you and me going out, only weirder.
那像是你跟我在交往 只不过更奇怪

74
00:05:29,890 --> 00:05:31,950
I know you're hurting..
我知道你很难过 我也想安慰你…

75
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:34,190
but don't say that again.
但别再那么说了

76
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:40,100
What if they marry? He'd be the stepfather of my child.
如果他们结婚了呢？ 他可能是我孩子的继父

77
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:42,430
You don't need to worry.
你不必担心

78
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:45,140
He'll never tell her how he feels.
他不会告诉她他的感觉

79
00:05:45,410 --> 00:05:48,270
If he did, you don't know how she'd react.
就算他说了 你不知道她会有什么反应

80
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:52,470
Sure, women never like Joey. I think he's a virgin.
女人从来就不喜欢乔伊 我想他是个处男

81
00:05:53,450 --> 00:05:57,480
-He isn't thinking about going for her. -He's not?
-他不想追她 -真的吗？

82
00:05:57,750 --> 00:06:01,420
All he's thinking about is how you're taking this.
他只想到你的感觉

83
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:05,590
It's freaking him out. He wants to move to Vermont.
这把他吓坏了 他想搬到佛蒙特去

84
00:06:06,590 --> 00:06:10,120
-Why? -He wants to leave the country.
-为什么？ -他想离开这个国家

85
00:06:14,740 --> 00:06:16,600
He thinks you hate him.
他认为你恨他

86
00:06:17,810 --> 00:06:19,360
Hate him?
恨他？

87
00:06:20,810 --> 00:06:23,500
No, I don't hate him.
不，我不恨他

88
00:06:26,010 --> 00:06:28,950
It's just, it's Rachel. You know?
她是瑞秋，你知道吗？

89
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:33,280
I can't even imagine how hard this must be for you..
我无法想像你有多难过…

90
00:06:33,490 --> 00:06:37,480
but I don't want you to lose Joey over it.
但我不希望你跟乔伊 因此做不成朋友

91
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:42,130
Right now, he needs to know that you're still his friend.
现在他得知道 你还是他的朋友

92
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:46,430
Okay, I'll talk to him.
好吧，我会跟他谈

93
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:48,330
I'd do it soon.
你最好快去

94
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:53,470
He just asked me how to convert his dollars into Vermont money.
他问我怎么把美金 换成佛蒙特货币

95
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,840
-Hi! -Hi.
-嗨 -嗨

96
00:07:02,050 --> 00:07:05,450
-Chandler, Monica, this is Don. -Hello.
-钱德，摩妮卡，他是唐 -哈

97
00:07:05,620 --> 00:07:07,650
Hello, nice to meet you. How are you?
哈，很高兴能认识你 你好吗？

98
00:07:07,820 --> 00:07:09,450
Soul mate.
心灵伴侣

99
00:07:12,490 --> 00:07:15,990
-What are you guys doing? -We had lunch at Adriatica.
-你们做了什么？ -我们在艾德瑞提卡吃午餐

100
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:20,860
-What's with the sun-dried tomatoes? -I know! Is this 1985?
-蕃茄干是怎么了？ -我知道，它是1985年的吗？

101
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:24,770
-That's what I said! Isn't it strange? -Not really.
-我就是那么说的，这很奇怪吧？ -一点都不会

102
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:28,670
What's wrong with sun-dried tomatoes?
蕃茄干是怎么了？

103
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:33,380
On a barbecued-chicken pizza?
在烤鸡披萨上吗？

104
00:07:33,610 --> 00:07:35,050
No?
不是吗？

105
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:40,080
-What restaurants do you like? -Octavio. 27-and-7.
-你喜欢哪家餐厅？ -奥克塔维欧，27与7

106
00:07:40,290 --> 00:07:44,620
-There's this place, Alessandro's. -Oh, my God! I'm the chef!
-还有亚利山多洛斯 -天啊，我是那里的主厨

107
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:47,690
You're kidding! Your food is fantastic!
你是在开玩笑 你做的菜好吃极了

108
00:07:47,930 --> 00:07:52,030
I want to talk about your menu. Anyone want coffee?
我要跟你谈谈你的菜单 有人要喝咖啡吗？

109
00:07:52,230 --> 00:07:55,500
If you're talking about me, I'll go with you.
我要喝拿铁，如果你要谈我的事 我跟你一起去

110
00:07:57,810 --> 00:07:58,900
I'll have a mocha-ccino.
我要喝摩卡奇诺

111
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:08,180
What are you doing?
你在做什么？

112
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:12,450
I swear, I didn't know you guys would be here.
我发誓我不知道你们在这里

113
00:08:12,690 --> 00:08:15,120
You don't believe in soul mates, so..
你不相信心灵伴侣，所以…

114
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:19,280
I believe in handsome strangers who hit on my wife.
我相信英俊的陌生人追我的老婆

115
00:08:19,490 --> 00:08:24,690
Just because I think they're soul mates doesn't mean anything'll happen.
虽然我认为他们是心灵伴侣 那不代表会发生什么事

116
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:27,260
Phoebe? Good work.
菲比？ 做的好

117
00:08:27,470 --> 00:08:30,130
He's great. I love him.
他很棒，我爱他

118
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:35,770
Don't worry, we'll find you someone else.
别担心 我们会帮你找到对象

119
00:08:48,820 --> 00:08:52,620
I understand if you came by to hit me. I deserve it.
如果你是来打我的，我了解 这是我活该

120
00:08:52,830 --> 00:08:55,130
No, I don't want to hit you.
不，我不想打你

121
00:08:55,330 --> 00:08:57,820
What, then? Kick me?
什么？你要踢我？

122
00:08:58,170 --> 00:08:59,390
No.
不

123
00:09:00,370 --> 00:09:02,130
Bite me?
咬我？

124
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,360
I don't want to do anything to you.
我不想对你怎么样

125
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:08,840
I just want to say I'm not mad at you..
我只是要说 我没有生你的气…

126
00:09:10,310 --> 00:09:13,610
and that I certainly do not hate you.
我当然也不恨你

127
00:09:14,820 --> 00:09:17,410
I just came here to say that.
我只是来告诉你

128
00:09:17,650 --> 00:09:19,980
Hey, wait, Ross?
等一下，罗斯

129
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:25,120
You wanna come in for a beer or something?
你想进来喝瓶啤酒吗？

130
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,330
Yeah, sure.
好吧

131
00:09:33,130 --> 00:09:35,730
You got any beer?
你有啤酒吗？

132
00:09:38,570 --> 00:09:41,840
All I got is melon stuff that Rachel left.
我只有瑞秋留下香瓜饮料

133
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,640
Okay.
好吧

134
00:09:51,290 --> 00:09:54,410
You need to understand something.
你得了解一件事

135
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:02,690
I am never gonna act on this Rachel thing, okay?
我不会对瑞秋采取行动，好吧？

136
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:07,730
I wouldn't do anything to jeopardize my friendship with you.
我不会做出任何 会危及你我友谊的事

137
00:10:08,970 --> 00:10:10,560
Thank you.
谢谢

138
00:10:27,090 --> 00:10:31,420
Anyway, it'll just..
总之我只是…

139
00:10:31,590 --> 00:10:34,990
It'll take me a while to get over her.
我得花点时间去遗忘它

140
00:10:35,260 --> 00:10:39,390
I'm not sure how to do that. I've never been in love, so..
我不确定我该怎么做 我没有陷入爱河过，所以…

141
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:41,120
What?
什么？

142
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:46,260
You're in love with her?
你爱上她了？

143
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:51,210
-Yeah. I thought you knew that. -No.
-对，我以为你知道 -不

144
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:57,520
Look, if it helps, I don't want to feel this way, honest.
听着，如果有帮助的话 我真的也不希望自己有那种感觉

145
00:10:57,750 --> 00:11:02,120
I just keep thinking, "I'll get over this, " you know?
我只是一直在想 “我得忘了这件事”，你知道吗？

146
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:06,290
But it just keeps getting harder.
但我越这么想就越忘不了

147
00:11:06,490 --> 00:11:09,950
I don't know what to do, you know?
我不知道该怎么办

148
00:11:11,470 --> 00:11:13,590
What do I do?
我该怎么办？

149
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:25,610
-You need to tell her how you feel. -That's the green stuff talking.
-你得告诉她你的感觉 -那一定是饮料害你这么说的

150
00:11:27,620 --> 00:11:31,110
I'm serious. You need to find out where she is.
我是认真的 你得知道她的感觉

151
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:35,250
If she's not where you are, you can start to move on.
如果她不喜欢你 你可以继续往前走

152
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:38,650
But what if, and I'm not saying she will be..
但如果 我不是说她会…

153
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:42,190
If she is where you are..
如果她喜欢你…

154
00:11:44,700 --> 00:11:48,970
then my feeling weird shouldn't stand in the way.
我的尴尬感觉不该妨碍你们

155
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:52,030
-Are you sure? -Yeah.
-你确定？ -对

156
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:56,170
If she ends up with somebody else..
如果她会跟别的男人在一起…

157
00:11:56,410 --> 00:12:00,280
the truth is, she couldn't find a better guy.
说真的 她找不到更好的人选

158
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:02,850
Hey, thanks.
谢谢

159
00:12:04,150 --> 00:12:09,420
-So when are you gonna talk to her? -Oh, my God. I have to tell her.
-你什么时候要跟她谈？ -天啊，我得跟她谈

160
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:14,020
I haven't thought about it. What should I say?
我还没有想过 我该说什么？

161
00:12:14,230 --> 00:12:18,060
I'm understanding, but let's not get carried away.
我能体谅你 但我们别太过份了

162
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,600
What am I gonna say?
我该说什么？

163
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:29,000
Yeah, tell me about it.
你说的对

164
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:48,290
I'm phasing out the wine importing and focusing more on the cheese.
我解决了进口酒的问题 现在全力研究起司

165
00:12:48,530 --> 00:12:50,430
Cheese, you say?
你说起司吗？

166
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:54,000
That's some pretty smelly work, huh, Don?
就是那种臭臭的东西，唐

167
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:58,230
-Excuse me? -Cheese. It's smelly.
-对不起 -起司很臭

168
00:12:59,110 --> 00:13:02,600
You must smell a lot of the time too.
你一定也常常闻起来很臭

169
00:13:04,410 --> 00:13:09,040
Not really. But with cheese, I think the smellier, the better.
不会的 但我觉得起司越臭越好

170
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:13,950
Me too! Chandler hates it. I can't have blue cheese in the house.
我也是，钱德讨厌它 在家我不能吃蓝起司

171
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:17,250
And you're still married to him?
你还是嫁给了他？

172
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:27,130
I would like to go to France and eat nothing but bread and cheese.
我想到法国只吃面包跟起司

173
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:29,630
Not even bread. Just cheese.
甚至不要面包，只要起司

174
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,770
No, I want the bread.
不，我要面包

175
00:13:32,410 --> 00:13:34,400
And pastries.
还有馅饼

176
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:36,730
And pate.
跟小馅饼

177
00:13:37,110 --> 00:13:40,770
I'm really not high. I just used to be fat.
我不是真的兴奋 只是以前我很胖

178
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:45,110
I have a villa in the Loire Valley you can stay in.
我在罗亚尔谷有栋别墅 你可以住在那里

179
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,450
Is it made of cheese?
它是用起司做的吗？

180
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:53,990
No. A house made of cheese, wouldn't that be incredible?
不，用起司做的房子 那很不可思议吧？

181
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:57,060
-I'd move in tomorrow! -Oh, come on!
-我明天就想搬进去 -少来了

182
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:01,060
-Listen to this! -I'm so sorry.
-你听到了吗？ -对不起

183
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:05,600
-What do we do? -They both want a house of cheese.
-我们该怎么办？ -他们都要起司屋

184
00:14:06,310 --> 00:14:09,170
I don't know how you fight that.
我不知道你该怎么办

185
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:19,940
Okay, okay. I can do this. I can tell her how I feel.
好吧，我可以这么做 我可以告诉她我的感觉

186
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:22,520
Okay, stand up straight.
好吧，挺直腰杆

187
00:14:22,790 --> 00:14:25,660
Take a couple deep breaths.
深呼吸一下

188
00:14:27,290 --> 00:14:29,160
Look confident.
表现出自信

189
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:35,000
Joey? What's up?
乔伊，怎么了？

190
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:39,640
I came by because I want to talk to you about something.
我来找你 因为我想告诉你一件事

191
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,140
What's up?
怎么了？

192
00:14:41,310 --> 00:14:44,300
Here, in the hall? What are we, animals?
就在走廊上谈？ 我们是动物吗？

193
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:47,970
I'm late for a meeting. Could you make it quick?
我开会要迟到了 你能快点说吗？

194
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:51,810
I just came by to tell you that..
我是来告诉你…

195
00:14:52,190 --> 00:14:56,050
I want to have dinner with you.
我想跟你一起吃晚餐

196
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:59,020
Sure. Just tell me where to meet you.
没问题，告诉我到哪里找你

197
00:15:02,830 --> 00:15:04,350
Okay. That's good.
好吧，太棒了

198
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:07,900
That gives you a couple of hours to prepare.
这给你 几小时的时间做好准备

199
00:15:08,870 --> 00:15:11,430
Don't you people ever knock?
你们从来不敲门吗？

200
00:15:12,970 --> 00:15:15,770
I'd like to have Don and Phoebe over. Wouldn't that be nice?
我想请唐跟菲比过来 那真的很棒吧？

201
00:15:16,010 --> 00:15:17,440
Sure. Set it up.
没问题，你去安排吧

202
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:20,910
I'll just be browsing through the personals.
我只是在看找伴分类广告

203
00:15:22,020 --> 00:15:24,420
Are you okay? You're acting weird.
你没事吧？ 你有点怪怪的

204
00:15:24,650 --> 00:15:27,250
Yeah. Fine. Not perfect.
好吧，我不完美

205
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:29,390
But good enough.
但我够好了

206
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,450
Jeez, what's with you?
天啊，你是怎么了？

207
00:15:31,690 --> 00:15:34,720
I'm sorry, did you say "cheese"?
抱歉，你刚刚说“起司”吗？

208
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:40,400
-What's going on? -Phoebe says you and Don are soul mates.
-怎么了？ -菲比说你跟唐是心灵伴侣

209
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:43,870
I don't believe in that, but you two get along.
我不相信 但你们两个处得很好

210
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:49,370
I'll step aside if you wanna go with Don and live in a house of cheese.
如果你想跟唐住在起司屋 我可以退出

211
00:15:49,610 --> 00:15:54,710
-You don't believe in soul mates? -No, but I'm sure "tomahtoes" does.
-你不相信心灵伴侣？ -对，但我相信“蕃茄干先生”相信

212
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:59,110
I don't believe in soul mates, either.
我也不相信心灵伴侣

213
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:00,620
-You don't? -Nope.
-你不相信？ -对

214
00:16:00,820 --> 00:16:03,450
We weren't destined to end up together.
我们不是注定要在一起的

215
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:07,290
We fell in love and work hard at our relationship.
我们陷入爱河 努力经营我们的关系

216
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:10,220
Some days we work really hard.
有时候我们非常努力

217
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:15,060
So you don't want to live with Don in a cheese house?
你不想跟唐住在起司屋？

218
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:21,270
No, I've had second thoughts. Do you know how hard it'd be to clean?
不，我想了一下 你知道它打扫起来有多辛苦吗？

219
00:16:21,510 --> 00:16:23,980
-I love you. -I know.
-我爱你 -我知道

220
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:26,700
I'm gonna take you out to dinner.
我要带你去吃晚餐

221
00:16:26,910 --> 00:16:31,350
I found this place that makes the greatest jalapeno poppers.
我找到一个 做墨西哥辣椒卷最好吃的地方

222
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:35,110
No? They taste so good.
不？它们真的很好吃

223
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:44,920
It happens whenever Chandler touches my stomach.
钱德一摸我的肚子就会这样

224
00:16:45,130 --> 00:16:48,000
I'm worried the baby won't like him.
我担心宝宝不喜欢他

225
00:16:51,010 --> 00:16:54,300
-Are you okay? -Yeah, sure.
-你没事吧？ -没事

226
00:16:57,010 --> 00:16:59,810
Look, the reason..
听着，我…

227
00:17:01,950 --> 00:17:03,880
Is it hot in here?
这里很热吗？

228
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:07,350
Why don't you take off your sweater?
你为什么不把毛衣脱掉？

229
00:17:08,260 --> 00:17:10,310
This is a nice place..
这个地方不错…

230
00:17:10,560 --> 00:17:15,360
and my T-shirt has a picture of Calvin doing Hobbes.
我的T恤印了 卡尔文上荷比丝的样子

231
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:19,360
Oh, my God, really? Can I see it?
天啊，真的吗？我能看一下吗？

232
00:17:19,570 --> 00:17:20,830
Yeah, sure.
当然可以

233
00:17:23,670 --> 00:17:27,330
I wouldn't think Hobbes would like that so much.
我想荷比丝不会太喜欢

234
00:17:33,650 --> 00:17:36,210
How long have we known each other?
我们认识多久了？

235
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:38,320
Seven, eight..
七，八…

236
00:17:38,550 --> 00:17:41,150
Eight years. Wow.
八年了

237
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:42,890
A long time.
真的很久了

238
00:17:44,290 --> 00:17:47,230
But over the past few weeks, I..
但过去几星期以来我…

239
00:17:47,490 --> 00:17:51,990
Okay! Sorry about the wait, but it is mega-jammed in here.
好吧，抱歉让你们久等 今天客人真的很多

240
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,930
Our specials tonight..
今晚的特餐是…

241
00:17:54,170 --> 00:17:56,800
-Could you give us a second? -Sure.
-你能等一下再来吗？ -好吧

242
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,340
Second's up!
时间到

243
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:05,180
Not that kind of table.
你们不是那种客人

244
00:18:08,520 --> 00:18:10,010
So you were saying?
你要说什么？

245
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,250
I'm not sure.
我不确定

246
00:18:13,420 --> 00:18:18,050
You asked how long we knew each other, and I said eight years.
你问我们认识了多久 我说八年

247
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:22,730
Then the waiter came over and cut his tip in half..
后来服务生走过来 害他少了一半的小费…

248
00:18:24,530 --> 00:18:26,470
and now here we are.
我们说到那里了

249
00:18:26,870 --> 00:18:29,890
Yeah. Here we are.
没错

250
00:18:39,550 --> 00:18:42,520
I think I'm falling in love with you.
我想我爱上你了

251
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:46,240
What?
什么？

252
00:18:48,390 --> 00:18:51,260
I'm falling in love with you.
我爱上你了

253
00:18:59,530 --> 00:19:01,590
Who are you talking to?
你在跟谁说话？

254
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,970
Oh, you're kidding. It's a joke.
你在开玩笑，这是闹着玩的

255
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,940
Funny. It's funny!
真的很好笑

256
00:19:09,210 --> 00:19:11,270
I don't get it.
我不了解

257
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:22,210
Okay.
好吧

258
00:19:25,890 --> 00:19:27,550
Wow.
哇

259
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:31,290
Okay, so the specials are..
今天的特餐是…

260
00:19:40,710 --> 00:19:42,440
Are you..?
你…

261
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:48,080
How did..?
怎么会…

262
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:50,410
When?
什么时候？

263
00:19:52,790 --> 00:19:55,250
Does it really matter?
那真的重要吗？

264
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,760
Wow. Wow.
哇

265
00:19:59,990 --> 00:20:02,190
It is hot in here.
这里好热

266
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:04,130
I know this is a lot.
我知道这真的很令人吃惊

267
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:07,630
You don't have to say anything.
你什么都不必说

268
00:20:08,770 --> 00:20:12,100
You take as much time as you need.
你要花多少时间思考都可以

269
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:21,410
Okay, you gotta say something.
好吧，你得说说话

270
00:20:22,280 --> 00:20:26,840
Joey, I love you so much.
乔伊，我非常爱你

271
00:20:27,090 --> 00:20:29,150
-But.. -But.
-但是… -但是

272
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:31,450
Joey?
乔伊

273
00:20:31,730 --> 00:20:34,320
Right. Hey, that's..
对，那是…

274
00:20:34,630 --> 00:20:36,860
That's okay. That's fine.
没关系，真的

275
00:20:37,100 --> 00:20:42,000
It's pretty much what I was expecting.
我料到你会这样

276
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:45,960
It's no big deal, all right?
那没什么大不了的，好吗？

277
00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:52,940
-I think I'm gonna go. -Please don't leave like this.
-我想我得走了 -请不要这样离开

278
00:20:53,180 --> 00:20:56,910
You can't do this to a pregnant woman!
你不能这样对一个孕妇

279
00:20:57,780 --> 00:20:59,410
Don't start doing that.
别那么做

280
00:20:59,690 --> 00:21:03,210
You can't do that, because you're gonna make me..
你不能那么做 因为你把我弄哭了…

281
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:05,410
Oh, there we go!
我们一起哭吧

282
00:21:07,930 --> 00:21:11,020
-Can I? -Sure.
-可以吗？ -没问题

283
00:21:12,930 --> 00:21:15,490
Oh, Joey. I don't want to lose..
乔伊，我不想失去…

284
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:17,830
Hey, hey.
嘿

285
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:23,370
You can't, okay? Ever.
你不会的，好吗？永远不会

286
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:27,070
I'm so sorry.
我真的很抱歉

287
00:21:27,310 --> 00:21:30,370
Please don't be sorry.
请你不要那么说

288
00:21:30,620 --> 00:21:32,850
Okay? Don't be sorry.
好吧？别感到抱歉

289
00:21:41,430 --> 00:21:44,060
You know, I was only kidding.
我只是在开玩笑

290
00:21:45,330 --> 00:21:47,630
Yeah, that was a real good one.
对，那真的很好笑

291
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:01,310
-Is this your table? -Yeah.
-他们是你的客人？ -对

292
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:04,010
-You'll be here all night. -I know.
-你得在这里待上一整晚 -我知道

293
00:22:04,250 --> 00:22:06,850
I haven't even read the specials.
我连特餐内容都还没有说

294
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:08,820
What's the matter?
怎么了？

295
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:13,820
I don't know. I think maybe one of them is dying.
我不知道 我想或许他们之中有人快死了

296
00:22:16,330 --> 00:22:19,160
I kind of hope it's the girl.
我希望是那个女的

297
00:22:20,100 --> 00:22:23,230
The guy is really cute!
那个男的真的很帅

